item.title: CVE-2022-43421|2024-08-03T13:32:59.056Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20tuleap%20git%20branch%20source%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Tuleap Git Branch Source Plugin 3.2.4 and earlier allows unauthenticated attackers to trigger Tuleap projects whose configured repository matches the attacker-specified value.
